    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint, showroom condition and has been meticulously preserved. Every aspect of the car, from the flawless exterior paint to the pristine interior, looks and feels like it just rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, it is perfect, with a smooth engine and precise handling that reflects its low-mileage and expert care. This is a rare find for a discerning buyer looking for a vehicle in impeccable, like-new condition.",
