    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable and affordable way to get around? This vehicle is in fair condition and is ready to serve its next owner well! While it shows some honest signs of its journey on the road, it remains a solid, functional choice that delivers dependable performance. It's the perfect opportunity to own a well-known model at a price that fits your budget\u2014come see why this car is a great value!",
      "price": 20000.0,
